2025/12/15 10:08:54 INFO dspy.teleprompt.gepa.gepa: Iteration 2: Proposed new text for generate_answer.predict: ## Task Instructions
## Predict Iris Species Based on Petal and Sepal Dimensions

## Task Description
Predict the Iris species based on the provided petal length, petal width, sepal length, and sepal width dimensions in centimeters.

## Input Format
### petal_length (cm)
Float value representing the length of the petal.

### petal_width (cm)
Float value representing the width of the petal.

### sepal_length (cm)
Float value representing the length of the sepal.

### sepal_width (cm)
Float value representing the width of the sepal.

## Task Objective
The objective is to predict the Iris species (setosa, versicolor, or virginica) based on the given petal and sepal dimensions.

