Characteristics of the leaf shape (e.g. 'simple', 'compound', ' lobed', etc.).

### margin (string)
Characteristics of the leaf margin (e.g. 'smooth', 'serrated', 'denticulate', etc.).

### apex (string)
Characteristics of the leaf apex (e.g. ' acute', ' obtuse', 'retuse', etc.).

## Task Objective
